snippet.title: Action Soccer gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Action Soccer, Dos PC game produced by UBI Soft in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/action-soccer/1464/
Playing the first match of the Ubi cup in this funny arcade soccer game from mid nineties.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
